net.minecraftforge.forgespi.language

インタフェース IModLanguageProvider

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    FMLJavaModLanguageProvider, MinecraftModLanguageProvider

    public interface IModLanguageProvider
    Loaded as a ServiceLoader, from the classpath. ExtensionPoint are loaded from the mods directory, with the FMLType META-INF of LANGPROVIDER. Version data is read from the manifest's implementation version.
